      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "A very very long time after, I come to make an update, I hope my comment will be read : Now Dozer seems to be a dead, and a good option is to use MapStruct, it&#39;s easy (support annotations), fast (no reflection) and seems secure (at the moment). This is included in the @Pascal Thivent list although, but I advise it (even if I had some problems by using it along with lombok)."
