      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "<a href=\"https://github.com/DozerMapper/dozer\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">The project is currently not active and will more than likely be deprecated in the future. If you are looking to use Dozer on a greenfield project, we would discourage that. If you have been using Dozer for a while, we would suggest you start to think about migrating onto another library, such as: mapstruct, modelmapper</a>"
