      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Another one to add to the list <a href=\"https://github.com/amgohan/zebra/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">github.com/amgohan/zebra</a> : DIY objects mapping and use zebra for unified way to inject mappers.  for the sake of performance, you do objects mapping manually and don&#39;t know how organize your mappers. Zebra come with a simple and unified way to : - create your mappers - manage one way and reverse mapping in one class - register your mappers and reuse them anywhere in your application - manage deep mapping"
